		<!-- message -->
		<div>Make a macro for MELEE SWITCH<br />
<br />
This works real well for keeping the mob somewhat in the same spot.  Good practice is in a tunnel area like HoT.  Engage the mob and call in troops behind it.  They will push the mob toward you and you should keep backing up.  Try to stay in the center of the hallway.<br />
<br />
Once youre a lil bit down, call the switch and all melee should go on the other side of the mob.  That wil push it back the other way.  <br />
<br />
If its against a wall, just tell em to push off the wall.  Once its inthe center, tell them to even up.</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
