		<!-- message -->
		<div>Sometimes you have to keep the mob in the center of the room, when the room itself is pretty small.  Good example is Chardok fighting into the Royals.<br />
<br />
If you get em close to the walls and if there something near that wall, they tend to jump on up to the ceiling.  So you have to fight them away from the walls and there's no way to corner them.</div>
